</div>
<div class="marker-cell">
<div class="marker-cell-label">Essential fatty acids</div>
<div class="marker-cell-title">Omega-3 Index</div>
<div class="marker-cell-ranges">Optimal: <span>&#8805;8%</span><br>Insufficient: <span>4&#8211;8%</span><br>Deficient: <span>&lt;4%</span><br><br>Measures EPA+DHA as % of red blood cell fatty acids. Most US adults are in the 4&#8211;5% range.</div>
</div>
</div>
